examples.en: It is the female birds that build the nests.
The birds use small leaves for lining their nests.
The birds' nests are high up, safe from predators.
A cuckoo is able to lay in a range of different nests.
All ducks upholster their nests in the same singular manner.
The birds build their nests in reed beds along the river bank.
All birds of this species are programmed to build their nests in the same way.
